OL,3,CRussian court charges four men over
OL,4,CMoscow concert mass shooting
OL,6,FFour men have appeared in a on
OL,7,Fterrorism charges following an attack
OL,8,Fon a concert hall in Moscow that
OL,9,Fkilled more than 130 people.
OL,11,FThe men, who appeared before a Moscow
OL,12,Fcourt on Sunday, showed signs of
OL,13,Fsevere beatings as they faced the
OL,14,Fformal charges, with one appearing to
OL,15,Fbe barely conscious during the hearing.
