OL,3,CRussian court charges four men over
OL,4,CMoscow concert mass shooting
OL,6,FA court statement said two of the
OL,7,Fsuspects accepted their guilt in the
OL,8,Fassault after being charged in the
OL,9,Fpreliminary hearing, though the men's
OL,10,Fcondition raised questions about
OL,11,Fwhether they were speaking freely.
OL,13,FThere had been conflicting reports
OL,14,Fearlier in Russian media outlets that
OL,15,Fsaid three or all four men admitted
OL,16,Fculpability.
OL,18,FThe hearing came as Russia observed a
OL,19,Fnational day of mourning that killed
OL,20,Fat least 137 people.
