OL,3,CRussian court charges four men over
OL,4,CMoscow concert mass shooting
OL,6,FMoscow's Basmanny District Court
OL,7,Fformally charged Dalerdzhon Mirzoyev,
OL,8,F32, Saidakrami Rachabalizoda, 30,
OL,9,FShamsidin Fariduni, 25, and
OL,10,FMukhammadsobir Faizov, 19, with
OL,11,Fcommitting a group terrorist attack
OL,12,Fresulting in the death of others.
OL,14,FThe offence carries a maximum sentence
OL,15,Fof life imprisonment.
OL,17,FThe court ordered that the men, all of
OL,18,Fwhom are citizens of Tajikistan, be
OL,19,Fheld in pre-trial custody until May 22.
