OL,3,CRussian court charges four men over
OL,4,CMoscow concert mass shooting
OL,6,FRussian media had reported that the
OL,7,Fmen were tortured during interrogation
OL,8,Fby the security services, and
OL,9,FMirzoyev, Rachabalizoda and Fariduni
OL,10,Fshowed signs of heavy bruising,
OL,11,Fincluding swollen faces.
OL,13,FRachabalizoda also had a heavily
OL,14,Fbandaged ear.
OL,16,FRussian media said on Saturday that
OL,17,Fone of the suspects had his ear cut
OL,18,Foff during interrogation. ITV News
OL,19,Fcouldn't verify the report or the
OL,20,Fvideos purporting to show this.
