OL,3,CRussian court charges four men over
OL,4,CMoscow concert mass shooting
OL,6,FFriday's attack, claimed by an
OL,7,Faffiliate of the so-called Islamic
OL,8,FState group, is the deadliest on
OL,9,FRussian soil in years.
OL,11,FRussian authorities arrested the four
OL,12,Fsuspected attackers on Saturday, with
OL,13,Fseven more people detained on
OL,14,Fsuspicion of involvement in the
OL,15,Fattack, Russian President Vladimir
OL,16,FPutin said in an address to the nation
OL,17,Fon Saturday night.
OL,19,FHe claimed they were captured while
OL,20,Ffleeing to Ukraine, something that
OL,21,FKyiv has firmly denied.
