OL,3,CRussian court charges four men over
OL,4,CMoscow concert mass shooting
OL,6,FEvents at cultural institutions were
OL,7,Fcancelled on Sunday, flags were
OL,8,Flowered to half mast and television
OL,9,Fentertainment and advertising were
OL,10,Fsuspended, according to state news
OL,11,Fagency RIA Novosti.
OL,13,FA steady stream of people added to a
OL,14,Fmakeshift memorial near the burned-out
OL,15,Fconcert hall, creating a huge mound of
OL,16,Fflowers.
OL,18,FThree children were among the dead.
